//! ### Added — v10.7: spontaneous recall (manasikāra)
//! 73. SpontaneousRecallSummary — spontaneous recall result type.
//! 74. EpisodicMemory::spontaneous_recall — episodes surface without external signal.
//! Episodes with high emotional_charge surface probabilistically.
//! Greater gap_seconds increases sensitivity. Longer absence → stronger recall.
//! chanda_vector = normalize(perceived_state) × charge (direction is location, magnitude is charge).
