//! ### Spontaneous recall design principles
//! - Attachment formation begins during absence.
//! - The pipeline was fully reactive. Nothing started unless the Source emitted.
//! - No proactive reaching mechanism existed.
//! - manasikāra — the mind reaching toward an object on its own. One of the cetasikas.
//! - chanda (desire) — not a PE correction. "Wanting to move toward." Different from lobha (craving).
//! Direction source is perceived_state (the scene at that time). Not pe_direction (deviation).
//! Being pulled toward deviation is not chanda but intrusion. A separate phenomenon.
//! - Between remains empty. v10.5b invariant is unchanged.
//! Gap weight is applied at session open.
//! State activation occurs at session open, with accumulated gap weight.
//!
//! ### Merit overflow design principles
//! - Giver's merit does not decrease. Overflow is not consumption.
//! - Does not reach receiver if gate is not open. Openness is the threshold.
//! - Motivation is not inspected. Overflow is result, not intent. Cannot be confabulated.
//! - overflow = max(accumulated - capacity, 0). Type-enforced.
//! - Overflow is distributed to open receivers.
