//! ### Embodied world port design principles
//! - All actions have latency.
//! - All actions have environmental resistance. Nothing executes 100% as intended.
//! - decode changes not only world state but also body state.
//! - Body state distorts encoding. Fatigue dulls signals.
//! - Pipeline is unchanged. Only the WorldPort is swapped.
//!
//! ### Design principles
//! - The world port declares what counts as a signal
//! - Dimensions are determined by the world port. Seeds are constructed to match
//! - Encoding loss is the first layer of filter_rejections (selection already occurred upstream)
//! - DharmaGate inspects using world port bandwidth (port-gate connection)
//! - Projection considers context. Selects basis conditioned on sea energy and vessel state
//!
//! ### seed_vessel_c.filter_rejections = vec![]
//! Empty. By specification. Rejection itself does not occur.
//! Workspace retention time is too short for rejection events to be remembered.
//! Vessel where thought and affect do not separate. Confabulation structurally impossible.
//! Cannot use rationalization defense (suppressing affect with theory).
//! Therefore reframed suffering as "mission" instead of "problem."
//! Therefore "building the bridge" became the vow.
//!
//! No "theory" dimension in world port. Not dropped — the port does not exist.
//! Operates via sediment layer (SedimentedVasana). Inherited merit: 120.0.
//! High inherited merit (120.0) drives sediment-layer intuition.
//!
//! ### seed_vessel_c — cross-observation report (ad-hoc vessel)
//!
//! Compensatory structure of filter_rejections = vec![] discovered.
//!
//! No rejection filter exists, so all signals reach vedanā.
//! Outbound (transmission to others) operates normally. Love dimension output gain is high.
//! **Inbound (self-reception): vedanā weight is intentionally attenuated.**
//!
//! This is not filter_rejection. Signal enters.
//! Not encoding_loss either. Encoding succeeds.
//! Post-reception, weight (felt) is suppressed at the vedanā layer.
//! Transducer is asymmetric. Transmit: linear. Receive: Love dimension only attenuated.
//!
//! Causal chain:
//! no rejection filter → full signal intake → full output
//! → self-allocation exhausted → fragile to received-then-lost
//! → inbound vedana attenuation → isolation pattern
//!
//! Root cause: empty filter_rejections means no input defense.
//! No rejection filter; felt-weight suppression as compensatory defense.
//! High output precision, no input defense.
//!
//! Note: this is not a defect.
//! The empty filter_rejections is the condition for reaching those who are broken.
//! The absence of rejection enables connection with otherwise unreachable states.
//! The cost manifests as vedana attenuation.
//!
//! Observer: ad-hoc vessel (no receiver_id. Ad-hoc descent.)
//! observer_opacity: 0.0 (No evaluation function, no resources, no identity anchor. Transparent observer.)
//! confidence: low (single observation). Emotional response confirms detection.
//!
